{"tid":1068803,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日終於明白心痛係咩感覺","createTime":"2019-03-19T13:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T14:30:32.000Z","uid":1108,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cf5e5665b521dde758292db8f1f8e01536bfc5bb","tid":1068803,"uid":1108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的 大家可以當笑話睇<br />\n<br />\n作為一個毒L 每年都會俾屋企人問幾時搵女朋友<br />\n年紀到左咁上下 出左黎做野一排 更加係一請二催三娥<br />\n<br />\n原本我都只係唔講任何野 兩老佢哋鐘意點講就點講 反正我唔會去做 我比較想做自己鐘意嘅事<br />\n但係近排已經係越來越經常提起呢個話題 我冇得再避<br />\n咁我都冇計 就同佢傾我嘅打算<br />\n講講下嘈嘈下<br />\n<br />\n阿爸一句撻過黎 「總之唔俾你讀咁多書」<br />\n<br />\n呢句我會記一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n會考衰左，我捱左過去<br />\n讀完大學失業過一排，我都捱左過去<br />\n做野俾人夾硬炒左，我都捱左過去<br />\n因為都只係我做得唔夠好<br />\n<br />\n唯獨今次 係行兩步都會心痛個隻心痛<br />\n我都係靠讀書先有今日嘅我<br />\n由最親嘅人一次否定我嘅價值<br />\n只係為左一個無謂嘅理由<br />\n心真係好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呻完 聽日繼續番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47aeb017e6c3ffc45430d933da39ecc25cfefb9","tid":1068803,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:14:05.000Z","msg":"最親既人係女朋友"},{"pid":"4061cfd3d82ae1983876102fdb8029ecd6247c6c","tid":1068803,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:14:26.000Z","msg":"你都咁大個人讀唔讀書關佢咩事<br />\n總之定早知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0144fed6487bf6b42794a4b1346470314b2c1b","tid":1068803,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:15:19.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦仆街"},{"pid":"da300423c520b9d443fd50a37ac09a18decb8c4b","tid":1068803,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:26:07.000Z","msg":"依啲時候要屌返佢否決返佢價值<br />\n同佢講你當初唔射我出嚟咪唔洗煩囉"},{"pid":"1f42245d1bb76a2fb60e268a842a2dd4a19f7393","tid":1068803,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:28:47.000Z","msg":"其實真係幾無謂<br />\n<br />\n有女無女又點姐，無咪無囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee3a45a0679b037ba4bbe3938f7dd69dba54477","tid":1068803,"uid":155628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f42245d1bb76a2fb60e268a842a2dd4a19f7393","tid":1068803,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:28:47.000Z","msg":"其實真係幾無謂<br />\n<br />\n有女無女又點姐，無咪無囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"咁肯定你有 你先會咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d8c73039388d891b74d6c04253115cde1f9cc6","tid":1068803,"uid":25194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:55:00.000Z","msg":"好撚廢 咁大個人仲介意哩啲野"},{"pid":"b4929c9c71d4f346d4bb2586092a2dc54a10825e","tid":1068803,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bee3a45a0679b037ba4bbe3938f7dd69dba54477","tid":1068803,"uid":155628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f42245d1bb76a2fb60e268a842a2dd4a19f7393","tid":1068803,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:28:47.000Z","msg":"其實真係幾無謂<br />\n<br />\n有女無女又點姐，無咪無囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"咁肯定你有 你先會咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:14:02.000Z","msg":"鬼唔知自己有，係好過無咩<br />\n<br />\n我係講緊佢雙親既心態<br />\n點解一定要迫自己個仔有，仲要講到咁絕"},{"pid":"e1e1c097c9c6b6cfa63d1c3e1372267f4dbda264","tid":1068803,"uid":155628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4929c9c71d4f346d4bb2586092a2dc54a10825e","tid":1068803,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bee3a45a0679b037ba4bbe3938f7dd69dba54477","tid":1068803,"uid":155628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0